report_cell_virtual_align(25.10)              report_cell_virtual_align(25.10)

Name
       report_cell_virtual_align - Reports the cells that need to be virtually
       aligned

Syntax
        report_cell_virtual_align

       [-help]

       [-cell <cells>]

       Reports the cells that need to be virtually aligned.

Parameters
       -cell <cells>
              Specifies the lib cells that require virtual alignment.

              -help"  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and de-
              fault information for each report_cell_virtual_align parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man report_cell_virtual_align

